Package: wildxing
Title: An R package for optimal positioning of widlife crossing structures
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Guillaume", "Bastille-Rousseau", email = "gbr@colostate.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides a series of functions to characterize the importance of linear features for widlife movement and provide an algorithm to select optimal positioning of potential crossing structures.  
Depends: R (>= 3.3.2), sp, adehabitatLT
License: GPL (>=3)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1.9000
Imports: raster, rgdal, rgeos, Rsymphony
